title: Maryland Gov. Larry Hogan says he wants to go back to a sane GOP, not one that 'attacks people who don't swear 100% fealty to the Dear Leader' - Yahoo News
content: Maryland Gov. Larry Hogan says he wants to go back to a sane GOP, not one that 'attacks people who don't swear 100% fealty to the Dear Leader'  Yahoo NewsView Full Coverage on Google News
description: "I believe that there is a pretty large lane of sane Republicans, and they're looking for a voice," Hogan said on Sunday.
